{"data":[{"date":"10:51 22/06","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rudiger t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u0169ng g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do John Terry \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong khi \u0111\u00f3 David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p\u00a0h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Juventus.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chi-354-trieu-bang-mua-hau-ve-juventus-172-175920.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</span>, song Chelsea t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Daniele Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Daniele Rugani. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" title=\"trung ve Rugani cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-2112-Arsenal-chi-dam-tranh-hang-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c Sarri ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay Conte, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 lu\u00f4n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"455","checkdouble":"189240"},{"date":"10:09 22/06","title":"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng: \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ph\u00e1p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u2018\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u2019 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n EURO 2016 hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ed1 4 trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m nay theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i Dabble Bet \u0111\u01b0a ra. H\u1ecd x\u1ebfp sau Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u1ea7m l\u0169i ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/DT-Phap-toan-thang-Diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kylian Mbappe m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p vs Peru.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u0110N hay Brazil \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a th\u00ec Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C. Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dac v\u00e0 Peru d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m qua, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn trong t\u01b0 duy chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u00dac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y HLV Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-2-3-1 thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-3-3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Giroud v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho Ousmane Dembele, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Antoine Griezmann v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Corentin Tolisso - ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 l\u1ec7ch t\u00f4ng v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Paul Pogba v\u00e0 N&rsquo;Golo Kante c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Blaise Matuidi&nbsp;m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ch\u00ednh hai s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps thay doi chien thuat, dat niem tin vao Giroud\" title=\"Deschamps thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Giroud\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/chipu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Deschamps ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Giroud</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a Matuidi ch\u1ebfch b\u00ean ph\u00eda c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Giroud \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i Peru, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i khi Peru b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 h\u1edf, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tung ra nh\u1eefng &lsquo;mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh&rsquo; \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a HLV Deschamps khi tung nh\u1eefng &lsquo;qu\u00e2n c\u1edd d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c&rsquo; v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &lsquo;\u00f4ng l\u1edbn&rsquo; v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Les Bleus tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 Croatia. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Iceland, Argentina ho\u1eb7c Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 1 trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p. N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0110T&nbsp;Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 nh\u00ec B t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Thay-gi-sau-man-ra-quan-cua-cac-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A, c\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng B nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00ec th\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb1m trong tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u00f2n l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps l\u00e2m v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o lam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-phap-vs-peru.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\">Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (KT): Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n, Les Bleus ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p vs Peru: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Peru b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018-465-189196.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-phap-loai-peru-khoi-world-cup-2018-465-189196.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i tim c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 khi \u0110T Peru b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"454","checkdouble":"189241"},{"date":"10:56 22/06","title":"Hazard c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/mo-ve-qua-bong-vang-hazard-nen-roi-bo-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u1eed xem nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay n\u00e0o! Argentina c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah, Anh c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min, Ba Lan c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">May m\u1eafn song h\u00e0nh &quot;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&quot; \u0110an M\u1ea1ch...</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 gian nan v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eabn l\u00e0m sao t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Sau ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1eafng Armenia t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thua Ba Lan r\u1ed3i Montenegro, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 su\u1ea5t play-off cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u00ec.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 17 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t CH Ireland v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn play-off l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FIFA su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2016.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Dan-Mach-1-1-Australia-Eriksen-toa-sang-trong-doi-hinh-phan-dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen \u0111\u01b0a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t, \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong g\u1ea7n hai n\u0103m qua. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Peru ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i g\u00ec t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn thua, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u00e1n sai h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Peru x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi n\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1eady. May m\u1eafn ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u01b0 HLV 65 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Hareide c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-australia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00eau ca v\u1ec1 hai qu\u1ea3 penalty ph\u1ea1t h\u1ecd trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u01a1 so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 may \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t thua qu\u1ea3 penalty ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia Mile Jedinak, \u1ea5y v\u1eady \u0110an M\u1ea1ch xem ra v\u1eabn c\u00f2n may ch\u00e1n khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Australia s\u00fat 13 so v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, d\u1eabn 5-3 \u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Christian-Eriksen-Dan-Mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien,-khong-phai-anh!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">... nh\u01b0ng Christian Eriksen th\u00ec x\u1ee9ng d\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong \u00edt n\u0103m qua, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup ch\u1ec9 sau hai n\u0103m b\u1ecb Albania \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea7u r\u00eca Euro 2016 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng cho 24 anh t\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Eriksen t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi \u1edf khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Kevin De Bruyne c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh (209 vs 207).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 Spurs v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Harry Kane s\u00fat b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 c\u01a1m b\u1eefa, Eriksen \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m lu\u00f4n vai tr\u00f2 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi &ldquo;danh h\u00e0i&rdquo; Lord Nicklas Bendtner kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng bay \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec sau Eriksen l\u00e0 Nicolai Jorgensen v\u1edbi 8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/100907-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chu\u1ed7i 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Eriksen ghi 10 b\u00e0n, chi\u1ebfm 40% chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u00fa volley ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Australia mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 11 trong 11 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh trong 44 tr\u1eadn Premier League g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen &ndash; c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 9 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, 26 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2014, HLV Morten Olsen th\u1eddi b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Eriksen qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch cho ch\u1ee9c th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh Hugo Lloris, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Spurs, Eriksen thu\u1ed9c tu\u00fdp ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng, n\u00f3i \u00edt l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ecf, h\u00f2 h\u00e9t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/102431-13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch nh\u00e2n v\u0103n n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean k\u00e9o theo, \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n. T\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 1992 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru v\u00e0 Australia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba m\u1eaft gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady, r\u1ed3i anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1edf h\u1eefu Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e2u. \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i xa tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu Ph\u00e1p nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u00f2n \u00dac l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec5m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb anh h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel, Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR khi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"453","checkdouble":"189242"},{"date":"10:31 22/06","title":"Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG Ph\u00e1p.\r\n\r\n</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/6 (gi\u1edd Nga), \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp;ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i t\u1edbi N&rsquo;Golo Kante, &lsquo;m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t&rsquo; khu trung tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba cung dong doi Phap an mung ban thang\" title=\"Pogba cung dong doi Phap an mung ban thang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pogba v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. &ldquo;\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi N'Golo Kante, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ea1y kh\u1eafp s\u00e2n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t. C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Kante c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i v\u1eady. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.&nbsp; \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn, Kante \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Kante c\u0169ng gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh nh\u01b0 Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0110T Ph\u00e1p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a Pogba s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng \u0110an M\u1ea1nh. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Les Bleus s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out sau \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-421-189241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-toan-thang-diem-sang-trong-con-bi-cuc-cua-cac-ong-lon-421-189241.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n th\u1eafng: \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng trong c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn</span><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018, song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ph\u00e1p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &lsquo;\u00f4ng l\u1edbn&rsquo; c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap-465-189192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap-465-189192.html\">Ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Peru, Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span><br />\r\nV\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru, Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/pha-luoi-peru-kylian-mbappe-lap-ky-luc-trong-lich-su-dt-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-phap-vs-peru-461-189190.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 Peru (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o lam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"452","checkdouble":"189243"},{"date":"10:21 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-17h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Thanh-Hoa-vs-Binh-Duong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Thanh H\u00f3a vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng sau nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i SLNA, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 sa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed tinh th\u1ea7n. \u1ede ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Thanh ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2&nbsp;HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea1i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o sau nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m n\u01a1i h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch 4 tr\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1&nbsp; \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (3-3). Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, so v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1eeba qua, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Thanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 5, thua 6.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 3, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc; \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Minh T\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Hi\u1ebfu, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ofere.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng; Thanh Th\u1ea3o, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ng\u1ecdc M\u1ea1nh, Hu\u1ef3nh Ph\u00fa, Tr\u1ecdng Huy, V\u0103n V\u0169, D\u0169 \u0110\u1ea1t, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Romario.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"451","checkdouble":"189244"},{"date":"10:30 22/06","title":"Christian Eriksen: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u1eed xem nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay n\u00e0o! Argentina c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah, Anh c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min, Ba Lan c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">May m\u1eafn song h\u00e0nh &quot;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&quot; \u0110an M\u1ea1ch...</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 gian nan v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eabn l\u00e0m sao t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Sau ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1eafng Armenia t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thua Ba Lan r\u1ed3i Montenegro, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 su\u1ea5t play-off cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u00ec.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 17 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t CH Ireland v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn play-off l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FIFA su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2016.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Dan-Mach-1-1-Australia-Eriksen-toa-sang-trong-doi-hinh-phan-dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen \u0111\u01b0a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t, \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong g\u1ea7n hai n\u0103m qua. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Peru ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018, ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i g\u00ec t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn thua, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u00e1n sai h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Peru x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi n\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1eady. May m\u1eafn ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo; &ndash; V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u01b0 HLV 65 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Hareide c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-australia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00eau ca v\u1ec1 hai qu\u1ea3 penalty ph\u1ea1t h\u1ecd trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u01a1 so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 may \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t thua qu\u1ea3 penalty ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia Mile Jedinak, \u1ea5y v\u1eady \u0110an M\u1ea1ch xem ra v\u1eabn c\u00f2n may ch\u00e1n khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Australia s\u00fat 13 so v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, d\u1eabn 5-3 \u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Christian-Eriksen-Dan-Mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien,-khong-phai-anh!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">... nh\u01b0ng Christian Eriksen th\u00ec x\u1ee9ng d\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh h\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong \u00edt n\u0103m qua, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup ch\u1ec9 sau hai n\u0103m b\u1ecb Albania \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea7u r\u00eca Euro 2016 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng cho 24 anh t\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Eriksen t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi \u1edf khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Kevin De Bruyne c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh (209 vs 207).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 Spurs v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Harry Kane s\u00fat b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 c\u01a1m b\u1eefa, Eriksen \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m lu\u00f4n vai tr\u00f2 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi &ldquo;danh h\u00e0i&rdquo; Lord Nicklas Bendtner kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng bay \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec sau Eriksen l\u00e0 Nicolai Jorgensen v\u1edbi 8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/100907-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chu\u1ed7i 9 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Eriksen ghi 10 b\u00e0n, chi\u1ebfm 40% chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u00fa volley ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Australia mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 11 trong 11 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh trong 44 tr\u1eadn Premier League g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen &ndash; c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 9 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, 26 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi 2014, HLV Morten Olsen th\u1eddi b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Eriksen qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch cho ch\u1ee9c th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh Hugo Lloris, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Spurs, Eriksen thu\u1ed9c tu\u00fdp ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng, n\u00f3i \u00edt l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ecf, h\u00f2 h\u00e9t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/102431-13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christian Eriksen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch nh\u00e2n v\u0103n n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean k\u00e9o theo, \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n. T\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; b\u00ecnh d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 1992 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru v\u00e0 Australia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba m\u1eaft gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady, r\u1ed3i anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1edf h\u1eefu Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e2u. \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i xa tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu Ph\u00e1p nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u00f2n \u00dac l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. C\u01a1 m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c \u1edf World Cup, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec5m v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Christian Eriksen, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb anh h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0110an M\u1ea1ch &ldquo;ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel, Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR khi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"450","checkdouble":"189245"},{"date":"11:01 22/06","title":"R\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh g\u1eb7p Panama: Sterling l\u00e2m nguy","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u1eeba b\u1ecb l\u1ed9, theo \u0111\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00e0 Southgate d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Raheem Sterling.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama b\u1ecb r\u00f2 ri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama b\u1ecb r\u00f2 ri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Panama. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/jordan-henderson-phat-bieu-hung-hon-truoc-tran-gap-panama-421-189237.html\" target=\"_blank\">Henderson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Panama</span>, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool tin Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 HLV Southgate s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, HLV Gareth Southgate c\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sterling v\u00e0 Alli l\u00e2m nguy</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Harry Kane tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf ph\u00fat 68.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling va Southgate\" title=\"Sterling v\u00e0 Southgate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/eng1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb Southgate \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcus Rashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Sterling \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Kane tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho Sterling. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDele Alli c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Ruben Loftus-Cheek nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Dele Alli \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn \u1edf h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Rashford hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tam s\u01b0 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"449","checkdouble":"189246"},{"date":"10:57 22/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 22/6: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/bai-du-thi-co-mot-ky-world-cup-qua-khe-cua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (22/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Steve Holland trong l\u00fac d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 ra t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y ghi ch\u00e9p bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp. C\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea1i t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 Anh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u00ec Raheem Sterling s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Marcus Rashford. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Dele Alli, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ruben Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/1-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-danh-bai-argentina-465-189201.html\" target=\"_blank\">Modic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft kho\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t Messi</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric cho bi\u1ebft Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt nh\u1eb1m kho\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t Lionel Messi khi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. Trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Messi ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n tung c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi so v\u1edbi 11 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Leo \u1edf tr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 Iceland.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Argentina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 phong to\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t Messi, ng\u0103n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec h\u01a1n. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3&quot;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/1-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Hummels kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup, trung v\u1ec7 Mats Hummels m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&rdquo;, Hummels n\u00f3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Eriksen gh\u00e9t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb Australia c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup sau khi VAR x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Poulsen \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay gi\u00fap Australia h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 11m g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Poulsen tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd x\u1eed t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng penalty, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Poulsen&rdquo;, Eriksen b\u1ee9c x\u00fac.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel, Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR khi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Khedira su\u00fdt b\u1ecb ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 t\u00ean Ludvig Holmberg trong l\u00fac ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn s\u00e2n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n Sami Khedira \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch l\u1eeba Khedira b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch trao cho anh m\u1ed9t &ldquo;m\u00f3n qu\u00e0&rdquo;, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 bay v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edbm v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Khedira t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/7 (sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup).</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"448","checkdouble":"189247"},{"date":"11:18 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Costa Rica vs Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil bu\u1ed9c ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t hay kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</strong> (+1 3/4)<br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Costa Rica vs Brazil<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian</em>: 19h ng\u00e0y 22/6<em><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m:</em> S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Costa Rica 0.86*1 3/4:0*-0.92 Brazil<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 1.00*2 1/2*0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-costa-rica-vs-brazil-va-du-doan-soi-keo-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil 19h ng\u00e0y 22/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nBrazil kh\u00f3 th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 nh\u01b0ng chung cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1. Selecao v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho ngay ph\u00fat 20 song c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Zuber \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00fa s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n n\u00e0y, Brazil ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. Nh\u01b0ng ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba l\u1ea1i ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. C\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar khong dong gop nhieu vao loi choi Brazil\" title=\"Neymar kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-neymar-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea7n l\u1edbn hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Brazil. H\u1ecd v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. S\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Selecao ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3 v\u00e0o Coutinho trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Gabriel Jesus b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, Willian, Paulinho xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f2n Neymar b\u1ecb k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p s\u00e1t sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ef3 l\u1ee3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 bao g\u1ed3m 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecbt kh\u00e1 k\u00edn c\u00e1c ng\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas. Sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 thua 0-1 t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Kolarov.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kolarov da phat thanh ban\" title=\"Kolarov da phat thanh ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Cham-diem-Costa-Rica-0-1-Serbia-Nguoi-hung-Kolarov-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 thua 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Kolarov</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil, gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u00f3 quy \u01b0\u1edbc ri\u00eang. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Brazil. Nghe ch\u1eebng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Selecao s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Costa Rica th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 ch\u1ee7 quan. M\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Argentina th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Brazil c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd trong c\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- Brazil thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n<br>\r\n- Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>Costa Rica (+1 3/4)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Brazil \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng. Costa Rica th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Serbia kh\u00f4ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ecdn phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n hu\u1ed1ng chi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 Selecao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Costa Rica, c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 pha t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Mitrovic d\u00f9 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia Costa Rica\" title=\"Serbia Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/tong-hop-costa-rica-vs-serbia-world-cup-2018-h1.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Brazil s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc kh\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi s\u1edbm l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. C\u00e1i c\u00e1ch ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng ngay sau khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng n\u01a1i HLV Tite.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Brazil kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 Tite mong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u01a1n, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Brazil d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea1ch ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica? Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Costa Rica vs Brazil c\u1ee7a Bongda24h tin tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi<br>\r\n- Brazil ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n sau 9 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 2 1/2)</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</strong> (+1 3/4)<br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 1-0</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 9 (U9 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Costa Rica trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 4 (+4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Costa Rica trong hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 2 (+2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 (O 3)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Costa Rica s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"447","checkdouble":"189250"},{"date":"11:23 22/06","title":"3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/3-nguyen-nhan-khien-argentina-cua-messi-tham-bai-tai-world-cup-truoc-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1edd v\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>Messi b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Argentina c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf CLB Barcelona. Tuy nhi\u00ean, El Pulga c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Messi v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 v\u00e2y r\u00e1p t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iceland. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 &lsquo;b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft&rsquo; Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Argentina 0-3 Croatia 3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Argentina 0-3 Croatia 3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Du-am-Argentina-0-3-Croatia-3-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Messi lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Argentina 0-3 Croatia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng lu\u00f4n theo s\u00e1t Messi, m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n v\u00e2y r\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Messi ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 20 l\u1ea7n, con s\u1ed1 th\u1ea5p th\u1ee9 hai b\u00ean ph\u00eda nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&nbsp;Argentina. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&lsquo;\u0110\u00f3i b\u00f3ng&rsquo;, l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i nguy h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, k\u00e9o theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Albicelestes sau sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Caballero trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a HLV Sampaoli<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh 'tr\u1ea3m' 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean Marcos Rojo, Lucas Biglia, Angel Di Maria, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Iceland. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y c\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt khi cho \u0110T Argentina thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Argentina \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tam S\u01b0, v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch r\u1eadp khu\u00f4n m\u00e1y m\u00f3c n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sampaoli\" title=\"Sampaoli\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/sam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Sampaoli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf HLV Gareth Southgate c\u00f2n mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i &lsquo;m\u00e0i gi\u0169a&rsquo; n\u00f3 t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup, trong khi v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 y\u1ebfu, \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Albicelestes d\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3, trong khi Croatia&nbsp;l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby \u0111\u00e3 gi\u0103ng s\u1eb5n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t, Croatia ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 s\u1eafc b\u00e9n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Perisic hay b\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Mandzukic nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n &lsquo;s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 dao&rsquo; c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 sa\u0301ng ta\u0323o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u00e2\u0323c nh\u00e2\u0301t th\u00ea\u0301 gi\u01a1\u0301i hi\u00ea\u0323n ta\u0323i la\u0300 Rakitic va\u0300 Mordri. N\u1ebfu chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0110T Argentina <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 cho k\u1ef3<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"> World Cup</span> l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p M10. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m xi\u1ebfc v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1ecfi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG Argentina, Messi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i t\u00ecm chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Argentina tham bai truoc Croatia\" title=\"DT Argentina tham bai truoc Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Sime-Vrsaljko-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Argentina-day-phu-phang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Argentina \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Aguero \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u01a1m b\u00f3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong tay Jorge Sampaoli l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 khao kh\u00e1t c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Mauro Icardi, Diego Perotti, Erik Lamela hay Ezequiel Lavezzi,&hellip; tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Salvio, Enzo Perez hay Marcos Acuna ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho M10. N\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u00f4m qua c\u00f2n Argentina ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac n\u1ebfu Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nigeria \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cho M10 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong tay h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-tham-hai-cua-argentina-trong-tran-thua-croatia-421-189203.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Messi-can-lam-gi-de-ngan-Argentina-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-tham-hai-cua-argentina-trong-tran-thua-croatia-421-189203.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina trong tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Argentina vs Croatia 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-argentina-than-khoc-het-nhu-dan-ba-421-189233.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sao-croatia-argentina-than-khoc-het-nhu-dan-ba.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-argentina-than-khoc-het-nhu-dan-ba-421-189233.html\">Sao Croatia: &ldquo;Argentina than kh\u00f3c h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 l\u0169 \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nSime Vrsaljko ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi than kh\u00f3c h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 Croatia c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-nigeria-muon-loai-argentina-o-luot-dau-cuoi-cung-421-189238.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sao-nigeria-muon-loai-argentina-o-luot-dau-cuoi-cung.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-nigeria-muon-loai-argentina-o-luot-dau-cuoi-cung-421-189238.html\">Sao Nigeria mu\u1ed1n lo\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\nFrancis Uzoho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iceland vs Nigeria, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"446","checkdouble":"189251"},{"date":"07:38 22/06","title":"B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Australia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/bang-c-world-cup-2018-co-hoi-nao-de-dt-australia-di-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Peru sau hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc dien bang C World Cup 2018 sau hai tran.\" title=\"C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bang-c-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 sau hai tr\u1eadn.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111ang n\u1eafm \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng sau. &quot;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&quot; ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 trong tay, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Peru d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin y\u00eau c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 theo l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Ricardo Gareca.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, Australia r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111ang \u1edf th\u1ebf &quot;c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi&quot; so v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Australia?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 Australia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Peru, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p. Hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Australia van con co hoi de gianh ve vao vong loai truc tiep tai bang C World Cup 2018.\" title=\"\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bang-c-world-cup-2018-co-hoi-nao-de-dt-australia-di-tiep.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n* \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng nhau (2).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean (0-2, 1-3,...). Australia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp khi h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Australia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hoa-australia-hlv-hareide-do-tai-do-cau-thu-dan-mach-met-moi-465-189187.html\">H\u00f2a Australia, HLV Hareide \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-australia-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-dan-mach-465-189184.html\">HLV Bert van Marwijk: L\u1ebd ra \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y Australia ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chuot-tui-xuat-hien-tren-khan-dai-465-189183.html\">Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong ng\u00e0y Australia h\u00f2a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-australia-461-189181.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 1-1 Australia (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-19h-ngay-216-ve-di-tiep-cho-linh-chi-462-189131.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (19h ng\u00e0y 21/6): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho &ldquo;L\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo;?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"445","checkdouble":"189217"},{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/argentina-lo-sot-vo-voi-phat-bieu-cua-hlv-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Iceland, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng Argentina.</h2><h2>Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Croatia tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-bang-d-world-cup-2018-421-187428.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</span> gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng D n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Iceland s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p Nigeria v\u00e0 Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Argentina-lo-sot-vo-voi-phat-bieu-cua-HLV-Dalic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Argentina lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV&nbsp;Dalic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Argentina r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Iceland t\u1ea1i Rostov. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u00f2n b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, HLV Dalic cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c fan trung l\u1eadp. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, theo d\u00f5i Croatia ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</em></div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Croatia chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod trong khi Argentina quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eadp bu\u1ed5i cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Moscow tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u1edf s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Croatia th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong 2 ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec Argentina qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 m\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi C\u0110V \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Croatia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/sampaoli-bao-chua-cho-su-mat-tich-cua-messi-469-189213.html\">Sampaoli nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-tham-croatia-argentina-phai-lam-gi-de-vuot-qua-vong-bang-421-189208.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Croatia, Argentina ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"444","checkdouble":"189218"},{"date":"07:36 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-quang-nam-vs-hai-phong-17h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland ho\u1eb7c Nigeria m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Iceland r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 Iceland \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c \u1edf Euro 2016 khi x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Hungary nh\u01b0ng thua v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Iceland ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNha s\u1ef9 ki\u00eam HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Iceland ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArgentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat 19 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ghi th\u00eam r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIceland sau b\u00e0n thua v\u1eabn v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alfred Finnbogason. Th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson khi\u1ebfn Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Iceland c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Argentina, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Gylfi Sigurdsson hay Alfreo Finnbogason ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n Iceland th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria vs Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn 2 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng Argentina, Iceland ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfn xa gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-croatia-421-189189.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Argentina vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Iceland l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgrimsson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeri \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Victor Moses, Alex Iwobi, Kelechi Iheanacho hay John Obi Mikel.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Nigeria (22h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Chi\u1ebfn binh hay \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-(22h00-ngay-226)-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ngang ng\u1eeda so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Salisu Yusuf c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, song l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft d\u00ednh. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nigeria ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Croatia l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nigeria c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Francis Uzoho 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u00edt so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThua 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi Iceland. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Iceland cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Nigeria c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n Nigeria c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Iceland \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Nigeria ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0. 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi to\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iceland vs Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nigeria-vs-Iceland-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-1-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 1-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"443","checkdouble":"189219"},{"date":"07:42 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-quang-ninh-vs-khanh-hoa-18h00-ngay-226-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (V\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 18h00 ng\u00e0y 226 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/than-quang-ninh-vs-sanna-khanh-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14, danh s\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u01a1ng binh c\u1ee7a Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Vinicius \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u01a1, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Thanh Hi\u1ec1n, V\u0103n Khoa, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Nguy\u00ean Sa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eeda h\u1eadn \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. V\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 bi\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 do CLB\u00a0t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean nhau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u201cngang t\u00e0ng\u201d. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1 trong 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh: Tu\u1ea5n Linh, Tu\u1ea5n T\u00fa, M\u1ea1c Qu\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Huy, Vi\u1ebft Tri\u1ec1u, Nh\u1eadt Minh, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Huy C\u01b0\u1eddng, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, Edyson.<br>\r\nKh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a: Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, Nh\u1eadt Nam, Zarour, Duy Thanh, Trung Hi\u1ebfu, Toure, Qu\u1ed1c Ch\u00ed, Tr\u00f9m T\u1ec9nh, Ho\u00e0i An, Tr\u1ecdng B\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"442","checkdouble":"189220"},{"date":"07:44 22/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-226-khong-con-duong-lui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7nh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: G\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e0ng \u0111i v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf kh\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1p cu\u1ed1i TP.HCM, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua g\u1ed3m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (17h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/HAGL-Saigon.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u1ea7n&nbsp; gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL \u00edt khi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi. B\u1edfi khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, NHM c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi HAGL, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i c\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-2 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00fac n\u00e0y tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sai Gon vs HAGL\" title=\"S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi HAGL. 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n th\u1eafng 2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 sau 90 ph\u00fat so t\u00e0i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o, trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7&nbsp;Vincent Bossou. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i binh, HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2, d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec trong tay \u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e1ng lo nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 V-League. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u nay 22/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 15 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Lich-thi-dau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-15-vleague-2018-hagl-tro-lai-168-189175.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018: HAGL tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi-168-189139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\" />